```{r setup, include=FALSE}
source("tidyquantplot.R")
sd = eventReactive(input$update,{gsd(input$t,fdate = input$daterange[1],tdate = input$daterange[2])})
```

Input {.sidebar}
----------------------------------------

```{r}
textInput("t","ticker","AMZN")
dateRangeInput("daterange","Date Range",start =today()-180)
actionButton('update','Update')
```

Column 
----------------------------------------

### Chart 

```{r}
renderPlotly({
sd()%>%psd()
 
})
```


